# How to Create New Test Project to our Solution
1. In Solution Explorer Pannel click right mouse button on the Solution <Project Name>
2. In Context Menu select Add->New Project
3. In Add New Project popup window select Visual C# -> Class Library
4. Enter name <Project.Tests> and click OK

#How to Add References to our Project
1. Click Right mouse button on the References
2. In Context Menu select Add References
3. In Solution menu check your <Project> and click ok

#How to install NUnit
1. Click Right mouse button on the References
2. In Context Menu select Manage NuGet Packages
3. In Open window enter nunit in Search area
4. Click on Nunit and install it
5. Click on NUnit3TestAdapter and install it
